node.text: Bachelorettes in Quarantine 😂 We made this video months ago when the lockdown first began but kept it in the vault to celebrate the start of @clarecrawley journey! Incredibly proud to be a part of this group of brave, beautiful, kind, funny, and inspiring women! Heres to adding a new sister TONIGHT!! 🌹❤️ @tristasutter @schefftwaterman @deannastag @jillian.harris @alifedotowsky @ashleylynnrosenbaum @emilygmaynard @desireesiegfried @andidorfman @kaitlynbristowe @therachlindsay @bkoof @hannahbrown
